casebody.data:
OAKLAND COUNTY, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
State of Michigan, DEPARTMENT OF LICENSING AND REGULATORY AFFAIRS, and Michigan Indigent Defense Commission, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 158315
COA: 341172 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 27, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 17, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
